<h1 id='getting-credentials'>Getting Credentials</h1>
<p>To get initial credentials you can follow these steps:</p>

<ol>
<li><a href="https://developer.dowjones.com/site/global/request-trial/index.gsp">Request a Trial</a>.</li>
<li>A Dow Jones representative will reach out and help match your use case with our products.</li>
<li>You will receive an email with (depending on products)

<ol>
<li>API Key</li>
<li>User/Pwd</li>
<li>Tokens</li>
<li>Link to details</li>
</ol></li>
</ol>

<p>You can then use the relevant authentication method of your API to connect and specific SFTP or SSH connection details for feeds.</p>
